If you’ve ever wanted to talk, but I missed your message reach out again.
The void is loud, and sometimes voices get lost in the echo.
I read more than you think.
I see more than you know.
If something sits heavy on your mind or your soul speak.
Whether it’s a thought, a wound, or a question... my door remains open.
- Abysiel
